overview: “Happy Endings” are most definitely the objective for this bunch of horned-up masseurs, whose only mission on the massage-table is to get their clients hard, throbbing and ready for action! Indeed, it’s not exactly tired legs and aching shoulders that attract their interest, rather the big, inviting shafts and well-filled balls that are always quickly on display. Connor Rex and Ron Negba lead the way; as the STAXUS twinks prove once again that when it comes to a rub-down there’s nothing better than a tight-fisted, tight-arsed massage with a horny pal!
title: Massage Me 2
